      "title": "Badulai district Tamil vote for Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "During the Presidential election to be held in the Parliament tomorrow, the vote of a Member of Parliament of Badulai District will be given to President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Padulai District Member of Parliament Aravindakumar's reply will be given to President Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "Aravindakumar MP also said that he has clarified the central committee of the party he represents regarding this issue."
